description:
Southie/South End Room+Private Ensuite Bathroom + Amenities!

$2,600/mo (+ ~$100 utilities/WiFi)

Private bedroom + ensuite bath in a newly remodeled 2BD/2BA with in-unit W/D, dishwasher, central AC, and tons of natural light. 

Building perks: 24/7 concierge, gym, pool, grills, elevators, garage parking ($200/mo).

Unbeatable location: 30 sec to Red Line, buses (9, 11, 47), Blue Bikes. Walk to Whole Foods, SOWA, Seaport, and Southie markets.

No broker fee. Furnished or unfurnished option available!

Must be LGBT friendly, No Smoking, No Pets :(.
